Installation
------------

Multiple projects are generated: 

- energyml-opc
- energyml-common2-0
- energyml-common2-1
- energyml-common2-2
- energyml-common2-3
- energyml-resqml2-2
- energyml-resqml2-0-1
- energyml-resqml2-2-dev3
- energyml-witml2-0
- energyml-witsml2-1
- energyml-prodml2-0
- energyml-prodml2-2

Energyml-types can be installed with pip : 

```console
pip install energyml_prodml2_0
```

or with poetry: 
```console
poetry add energyml_prodml2_0
```
